From: Marcin FM <marcin@lgic.pl>
Subject: [PATCH] Use the generated builder in the doctest

The published example calls a builder setter directly on `Message::default()`.
Use the generated typed-builder API documented by the crate instead.

--- a/src/lib.rs
+++ b/src/lib.rs
@@ -43,7 +43,7 @@
 //! ```rust
 //! use serde_sarif::sarif::Message;
 //!
-//! let message = Message::default()
+//! let message = Message::builder()
 //!   .id("id")
 //!   .build();
 //! ```
